column16: Desmond Jennings grounds into a force out, fielded by third baseman Yangervis Solarte.   Yunel Escobar out at 3rd.
Ryan Hanigan singles on a ground ball to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Matt Joyce scores.    Yunel Escobar to 2nd.
Yunel Escobar singles on a line drive to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Brandon Guyer scores.    Matt Joyce to 2nd.
Chris Leroux intentionally walks Matt Joyce.
Umpire reviewed (tag play), call on the field was upheld: Brandon Guyer singles on a ground ball to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Sean Rodriguez scores.    Brandon Guyer to 2nd on the throw.
Sean Rodriguez doubles (5) on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.   Wil Myers scores.
Wil Myers singles on a ground ball to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Desmond Jennings scores.
Kyle Seager pops out to shortstop Derek Jeter on the infield fly rule.
Dustin Ackley singles on a line drive to left fielder Ichiro Suzuki.   Justin Smoak to 2nd.
Justin Smoak singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
Corey Hart flies out softly to right fielder Carlos Beltran.
